readable.content: A group of people stand together and look at the camera . A man , a woman , a girl , and a younger girl look puzzled and concerned . A man , woman and one girl face the camera , while one girl faces away . Oriental man , and two women facing camera and young child with back to camera . Three people looking concerned facing us , a girl in a backback facing away .
